'''盧森堡金融推廣署'''({{lang-en|Luxembourg for Finance}})，為主要推廣和發展成為[[盧森堡|盧森堡]]金融中心地位，盧森堡金融角色，主要由[[盧森堡政治|盧森堡政府]]和盧森堡金融業商會，以[[政府和社会资本合作|政府和社会资本合作]]（港臺譯作：民間參與公共建設）共同設立貿易一體，諸如位於[[盧森堡|盧森堡]]的盧森堡銀行公會<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abbl.lu/|title=The Luxembourg Banker's Association home|date=2020-02-26|website=The Luxembourg Banker's Association|publisher=Communication department of The Luxembourg Banker's Association|access-date=2020-02-26|archive-date=2012-05-11|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67ZyziIsE?url=http://www.abbl.lu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、盧森堡基金業協會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.alfi.lu/ |title=Association of the Luxembourg Fund Industry home |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2020-02-26 |website=Association of the Luxembourg Fund Industry |publisher=Communication department of Association of the Luxembourg Fund Industry |access-date=2020-02-26 |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427023902/https://www.alfi.lu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>或盧森堡保險和再保險業協會<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.aca.lu/|title= The Association of Insurance and Reinsurance Companies home|author= <!--Not stated-->|date= 2020-02-26|website= The Association of Insurance and Reinsurance Companies|publisher= Communication department of the Association of Insurance and Reinsurance Companies|access-date= 2020-02-26|archive-date= 2017-08-21|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170821174517/http://www.aca.lu/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gouvernement.lu/|title=gouvernement.lu // L’actualité du gouvernement du Luxembourg - Accueil|website=www.gouvernement.lu|language=fr|access-date=2017-03-14|archive-date=2011-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110226083234/http://www.gouvernement.lu/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.luxembourgforfinance.com/en/about-us/luxembourg-finance/profil-luxembourg|title=PROFIL Luxembourg|work=Luxembourg for finance|access-date=2017-03-14|archive-date=2019-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/w